rows.name:
Now rotten monsters know bashy-smashy
consequences of Nopon-bothering!

rows.label: qst711602_msg0003
rows.name:
Now Punpun can enjoy naps with
no fear to heart's content!

rows.label: qst711602_msg0101
rows.name:
Terrible bully has proper name
of Myrrhes Crustip. Punpun not
let that big bully off lightly!

rows.label: qst711602_msg0102
rows.name:
Monster's rotten friends are many
in swampy area around camp!

rows.label: qst711602_msg0103
rows.name:
Punpun's desire for vengeance
will be satisfied with
bashy-smashy of three of them.
